t flirting and sexting.<br />\nI cheated. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nAnd it hurt her badly, hurt myself badly for hurting her as well.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nI want her forgiveness, but that's a selfish act.<br />\nBecause that's what I want, not what she wants to give<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b34194f64f0479e2c1ae1d6505672a4f90fd853","tid":1220060,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:20:08.000Z","msg":"唔好犧牲 你仲要一齊見證住個政權點仆親"},{"pid":"f7a854aca4c52557f0eabc7b861bf478fa1eaea8","tid":1220060,"uid":45355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:32:11.000Z","msg":"我都係岩岩分手 加上見到自己既屋企變得愈黎愈衰<br />\n唉好亂好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc47763b86a6c2d8f6fed84535d52cc247b0365","tid":1220060,"uid":61989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T10:34:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3efc49da0730e7955dfbdedde53e403a555515f9","tid":1220060,"uid":160130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T11:43:07.000Z","msg":"就係因為612，去之前嗰一晚見返分咗手幾個月嘅女友， 想有危險之前講返啲內心說話。<br />\n<br />\n但可惜見完佢，佢仍然唔肯接受返我。<br />\n<br />\n我只係想講，對唔住，<br />\n要你一直為我受苦。我亦都真係改變緊。<br />\n<br />\n但我唔會放棄你，<br />\n同我唔會放棄呢個城市一樣。 <br />\n<br />\n儘管機會有幾細都好，一定會有轉機。<br />\n所以大家都要努力！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申:不過諗起佢，又真係好頹到想死&hellip;&hellip;"}]}